
label s163:
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "\"----\""
    
    "I glance at the clock."
    
    "It's already past nine."
    
    "I'd be late even if I went to school now---and to be honest, going with Arcueid is more fun than going to school...."
    
    "\"Alright."
    
    "I'll spend the day with you."
    
    "But if we go into the city during the day, I don't think there'll be any Dead around?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T01B.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"I don't care about that."
    
    "I just wanted to walk around, so even if it is daytime, it doesn't matter.\""
    
    "\"....?"
    
    "What, aren't we making up for last night and going to look for vampires?\""
    
    "\"Yes, of course we'll look tonight."
    
    "But to have you help me all day and night would be hard, so during the day I thought we could relax.\""
    
    "\"I think that'd be more fun too."
    
    "But, just the two of us walking around, that's....\""
    
    "like what they call a date in the real world."
    
    ".... Maybe you can't say that with a vampire like Arcueid, but I suppose she's telling me to take her out for some fun."
    
    "For me, I----I need to get ready mentally and.."
    
    "\"....?"
    
    "What's wrong, Shiki?"
    
    "Your face, it's turning red.\""
    
    "\"------Uh.\""
    
    "I cover my face with my hands and look away."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    ".... Certainly it's been just the two of us many times before."
    
    "But, those were emergency situations, and it was more like a pact of cooperation than anything between a man and a woman."
    
    "That's why----no matter how pretty I thought she was, I tried not to notice it."
    
    "But, if.."
    
    "Without any danger, without any purpose, if the two of us just walk around, I might notice something I never noticed before, and it makes me hesitate----"
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T11.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Shiki?"
    
    "Hey, are you going to school after all....?\""
    
    "\".... No way."
    
    "I said I'd do it, so I will."
    
    "I don't know what you're thinking, but walking around shouldn't be a problem.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T08.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Then it's decided."
    
    "Then let's go.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "She walks toward the window she snuck in earlier."
    
    "\"Wait a minute."
    
    "I'm going to change, so can you just look outside for a while?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T01A.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"What, did you call me?\""
    
    "\"Oh, yes, no!"
    
    "Just go outside, I'll be there soon.\""
    
    "\"Okay, I'll wait outside."
    
    "I've waited this long, so don't make me wait any longer, Shiki..\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "She jumps out the window with the lightness of a cat."
    
    "I hear the rustling of the trees outside."
    
    "She didn't jump to the ground, but along the tree branches."
    
    ".... With a body like that, it should have been easy getting in here undetected."
    
    "\".... This isn't the time to be impressed."
    
    "I too have to sneak out without Hisui noticing.\""
    
    "I change into some normal clothes."
    
    "Cracking open the door slightly, I look around to make sure no one's in the hallway and tip-toe outside."
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    stop music
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_32A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    play music 'sound/03.mp3'
    
    "Luckily, no one saw me as I made my way out."
    
    "Arcueid is looking the other way as she mumbles to herself."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_32A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T22.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Thanks for waiting."
    
    "C'mon, let's go Arcueid."
    
    "If we stick around here, Kohaku-san will find us.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_32A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T14.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Eh?"
    
    "Ah, yeah, we should go.\""
    
    "Completely different from before, her words seem very empty."
    
    "\"What is it?"
    
    "This isn't like you at all."
    
    "Did something happen again just now?\""
    
    "\".... No, nothing really.\""
    
    "I said the 'again' part strong, but her words are still hollow."
    
    "----It seems like she's planning something."
    
    "I feel kind of scared."
    
    "\".... Are you feeling sick because it's daytime?"
    
    "There's no need to force yourself to go out."
    
    "If it's hard for you, we can stop.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_32A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T03.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Mmh, I feel fine right now."
    
    "But seeing this wall reminded me of last night.\""
    
    "\"....?"
    
    "About last night, you mean while you waited for me at the park?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_32A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T04.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Yes,\" Arcueid nods meekly."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_32A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T03.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"I dashed here with all my strength and snuck into your room.... but it seems strange when I think about it now."
    
    "Why was I so angry back then?"
    
    "It was just a little promise.\""
    
    "Saying she doesn't get it, Arcueid crosses her arms in thought."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_32A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T02.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Ah, that's right."
    
    "Maybe you get it, Shiki?"
    
    "You always tell me I'm so stupid, so maybe you can understand?\""
    
    "\"Hey....\""
    
    "If she doesn't understand herself, then how does she expect me to?"
    
    "There's no way I understand, but if I have to respond----"
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_32A.jpg' at bgpos
    
